title: [Nielira Harbor, Aelerine Pier]
description: Sculpted posts of marbled grey stone flank the ebony-planked pier, each lantern-affixed column draped in coils of verdant ivy.  The vine-woven latticework arcs across the area, the flora-interspersed canopy suspending a vine-framed haon sign above the riveted dock, the rectangle swaying in the ambient breeze.  Aelerine-branded footlockers of ironwood and leather are neatly stacked beside the posts, the containers draped in layers of netting skimming the floor below.
